@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ijtniu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((0.97 / wp.exp(v0 + 0.49)))
    v1 = (v1 - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.28) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.21)))
    v2 = 0.29
    v1 = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = v1
    v1 = 0.92
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
